<HEADLINE>
<P>
HIGH SCHOOL VOLLEYBALL PLAYOFFS; 
</P>
<P>
PALISADES RALLIES IN THE FINAL GAME TO END GRANADA HILLS' BID FOR TITLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Granada Hills erased a nine-point deficit to tie the deciding game, but 
Palisades came back and secured a 15-12, 8-15, 6-15, 15-3, 16-14 victory in a 
City Section 4-A Division volleyball playoff match Thursday at Granada Hills. 
</P>
<P>
Granada Hills trailed, 13-4, in the final game before forging a 14-14 tie. 
</P>
<P>
