<HEADLINE>
<P>
SPOTLIGHT / COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE: FOCUS: BACK BAY COURT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Champion Development Co. has broken ground on Back Bay Court, a 24-unit 
specialty shopping center in Newport Beach. 
</P>
<P>
Scheduled to open in the fall, the $13-million center will include retail 
stores, service businesses and restaurants. About 15% of the center's space has 
been leased. 
</P>
<P>
FACTS AND FIGURES 
</P>
<P>
Address: Jamboree Boulevard and Bristol Street North, Newport Beach 
</P>
<P>
