</P>
<P>
Architect: Musil Perkowitz Ruth Inc. 
</P>
<P>
Broker: Tri-Pacific Commercial Brokerage 
</P>
<P>
Scheduled Completion Date: Fall, 1990 
</P>
<P>
Square feet: 35,000 
</P>
<P>
