England during World War II at the Simon Edison Centre for the Performing Arts 
in Balboa Park through June 10. Performances are at 8 p.m. Tuesday-Saturday; 7 
p.m. Sunday May 23-24 and June 5, and 2 p.m. Saturday-Sunday and June 6. LINDA 
