</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
FIVE-COUNTY COMPARISON 
</P>
<P>
Not only Orange County incurred a decline in single-family home permits during 
the first two months of the year. All four of the surrounding counties had 
lower numbers as well, led by the 35% drop in Los Angeles. The statewide total 
was also off the 1989 pace. And the five-county total dropped from 49% of 
January-February statewide action to 46% this year. 
</P>
